    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Superfamily Majoidea Samouelle, 1819, dorsal habitus:A, Mithraculus coryphe (Herbst, 1801), male, cw 8.2 mm (BLSZ 121); B, Mithraculus forceps A. Milne-Edwards, 1875, female, cw 15.4 mm (BLSZ 208); C, Mithrax hispidus (Herbst, 1790), male (juv.), cw 11.2 mm (BLSZ 029). Scale bars: A, B: 20 mm; C = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8129862/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8129867>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Superfamily Majoidea Samouelle, 1819, dorsal habitus: A, Nemausa acuticornis (Stimpson, 1871), male, cw 4.8 mm (BLSZ 057); B, Nemausa cornuta (de Saussure, 1857), male, cw 8.3 mm (BLSZ 210); C, D, Omalacantha bicornuta (Latreille, 1825), male, cw 10.4 mm (MZUSP 40898); male, cw 15.0 mm (BLSZ 213). Scale bars: A, B = 5 mm; C, D = 20 mm." ;
